\[\phi\left(\bm{x};\bm{w},\bm{v}\right)=\frac{1}{\sqrt{m}}\sum_{r=1}^{m}v_{r} \cdot\sigma\left(\bm{w}_{r}^{\top}\bm{y}\right),\] (2)

